Release 0.1.0  2017-08-06
- first release
- mostly for gcc C compilation C++ is missing so far
- CFLAGS and LDFLAGS can be set via header comments in the script file
- cache command available:  clear and list
- mach and arch dependend, so e.g. 32bit and 64bit Linuxes geenerate different
  compiled files to the same source file
- use a general config file $HOME/.cscript
- real document is missing
